Netizens responded, "This is the people being the masters of their own country."
"Why are there only uniformed ghosts on Halloween in our country?"
"Don't they have to go to work? Don't they have to work overtime?"

Medical staff at Baisha Health Center hung a banner at the door to demand their salaries and asked their leaders to get out of the hospital.

content:
November 1, Nanjing. The owners of Mingyue Fenghe went to the Lishui District People's Government to protest the unfinished house.
During the period, a leader came to warn the owners not to post videos randomly
The owner retorted, "Do you have any problems? If there are no problems, why are you afraid of (the people) taking pictures? Why can't you post it?"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On the night of November 1, the K7034 train from Heihe to Harbin derailed. There were no casualties in the accident and the cause is under investigation.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 2, Shaanxi Electronic Information Vocational and Technical College.
A student was beaten by his roommate. The student next to him said he would call the police, but the teacher scolded him loudly, "Why are you talking so much nonsense?"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
At 10 pm on November 1, a student protest broke out in a high school in Quanzhou, Fujian.
The school announced that classes would continue as usual on Saturday, which caused dissatisfaction among students. Hundreds of students gathered outside the administrative building to demand a weekend off.
In the end, the school announced that Saturdays would be changed to voluntary self-study at school, and the students celebrated the success of the "uprising".

content:
November 1, Chongqing. A woman cosplays as a mother of three with dark circles under her eyes.
Netizens responded: "It's Chinese horror indeed" and "I declare this the scariest cosplay for Halloween"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 1, netizens caught spies in the comment area. Question: One sausage costs 3 yuan, how much does two cost?
Another netizen answered: 6 yuan was suspected of being a spy. Because buying one more sausage will save one yuan, that is, 5 yuan.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: November 1, Ganzhou, Jiangxi. A student of Ganzhou Vocational and Technical College was asked to sign a "Internet circumvention commitment" for circumventing the firewall. He promised not to use circumvention software to access banned overseas websites and services, and was willing to bear legal responsibility if he violated the commitment.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, after her performances were cancelled one after another, Jin Xing posted a post on the evening of November 1, quoting famous sayings: "When ignorance is called the mainstream, being awake is a crime" and "When you get to know the people of this land in depth, you will find that their thoughts are worthy of their suffering." However, some netizens found that Lu Xun and Yu Hua did not say the words in the picture, and Jin Xing was also criticized by many positive energy bloggers. Later, Jin Xing set her Weibo account to invisible (now restored)

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, a campaign to "hang Mao Zedong's portrait" has been launched in campus dormitories across the country.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
November 1, Jinan, Shandong. Laiwu No. 1 Middle School has caused dissatisfaction among students because of the inconsistent work and rest time of each grade. For example, the evening self-study of the 63rd grade of the school is extended, while the 65th grade can have two and a half days off.
The students posted a big-character poster "Anti-traitor Manifesto" on the wall to protest the principal's inaction.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 1, Zhoukou, Henan. A woman posted a video saying that her BMW was secretly driven away by the staff of the local court, and there were millions of yuan of property in the car.
After calling the police, she learned that the BMW had become a vehicle to be executed, but the woman insisted that she had no case in her name. Even if she was the person to be executed, why didn't the court notify her before the execution.
At present, the court has not returned the vehicle and the property worth millions of yuan in the car.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 1, a netizen asked Doubao AI: Is it an insulting term for people in the Middle East to call the Chinese "Qinqiang poor"?
Doubao AI replied: This statement is completely wrong.
When the netizen replaced the country with the United States and Japan and called the Chinese "Qinqiang poor", AI replied: This is an insulting term.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: According to a report on October 30, a 10-year-old girl in Crimea posted a video on Tik-Tok. She attached an angry expression under the Russian flag and a love and sick expression under the Ukrainian flag. Afterwards, the local police determined that the girl was suspected of "insulting soldiers". Because the girl was too young, her 38-year-old mother will face an administrative case for "failing to fulfill the responsibility of raising and educating minors."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Hot searches on Weibo on October 30: 
Many men in Baoding beat up four female high school students
A 19-year-old boy in Nanchang stabbed a 22-year-old girl to death
Police officer accused of dereliction of duty for not filing a case of rape against a 12-year-old girl
A man attacked his wife with a knife during domestic violence, and his son stepped forward.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
November 1, Israel. According to local volunteers, Mr. Nie, a Chinese worker who was seriously injured in the Hamas attack on Israel on October 7 last year, can now eat with the help of the Israeli government and volunteers.
Not only that, the Israeli government has given this Chinese worker the same treatment as other citizens, and he can receive about 8,000 shekels of terrorist compensation every month.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 1, a report said that a 13-year-old girl in Xinhua County, Hunan Province was raped and lured into prostitution by multiple people. The main offender was 17 years old when he committed the crime. In addition to the main offender, 6 other minors who committed the crime were sentenced to suspended sentences. Another 3 public officials had sex with the girl after reaching a prostitution agreement with the main offender and have been dismissed from their public positions.
Ironically, the propaganda slogan on the roadside in Xinhua County: Sexual assault on minors can be sentenced to death according to law...

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 1, it was reported that the Afghan Taliban issued a new ban prohibiting women from speaking in public.
Hua Chunying had previously said that the Afghan Taliban was more sober and rational than when it was in power last time.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 1, the outer wall of Henan High People's Court was sprayed with red paint by depositors of village banks, saying "Dog officials must not die a good death, officials protect each other, collude with each other, embezzle, and pervert the law."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 1, Andy Lau went to Taiwan for a concert after 11 years. During the concert, he sang the song "Chinese", and the text on the screen was in simplified Chinese. This caused a lot of excitement among Chinese netizens.
Netizens replied "Taiwan returns, I support Andy Lau to be the governor"
"Andy Lau alone can retake Taiwan"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 1, Huanggang, Hubei. Students at Huanggang Foreign Language School posted big-character posters at school to protest against the half-day monthly vacation.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, a blogger exposed that Tongcheng Travel illegally sold points tickets, causing passengers to be denied boarding by airlines. Some passengers were even asked to pay for full-price tickets without discounts when they arrived at the counter. Passengers were unable to accumulate points or enjoy benefits during their trips, and if the points were not obtained properly, the parties involved might even face the risk of being sued.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
November 1, Shenzhen, Guangdong. Several urban management officers put oranges from vendors into plastic bags and took them away.
Vendor: The urban management officers want to eat oranges today.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, a large number of netizens have complained online that their bank accounts have been frozen, their legitimate income has been forcibly transferred away, and they have even been pursued because they sold second-hand watches or brand new mobile phones in stores.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Follow-up on the salary demand at Zhengzhou Baisha Hospital: Zhengzhou reported the "gathering of medical staff at Baisha Town Health Center": basic salary has been paid, and performance-based salary is yet to be paid due to hospital losses and other issues.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Lishui Mingyue Fenghe Community is still listed as for sale, although it is 60 kilometers away from the center of Nanjing, the selling price is still as high as 15,000 yuan per square meter. The second-hand price of nearby properties has dropped to more than 8,000 yuan.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: K7034 derailment accident This is the second derailment accident that has occurred in the Harbin Railway Bureau Heihe Local Railway Company in the past year. The last accident occurred in the early morning of October 15, 2023.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
November 1, Heilongjiang. Netizens posted a video to teach everyone how to identify enemy spies around you:
Send a well-known line to the other party, such as "Palace Jade Liquor". If the other party cannot answer the next sentence, then the other party is likely to be an enemy spy.
Ask the other party under what circumstances 1+1 equals 3, and how many steps it takes to put an elephant into a refrigerator. If the other party cannot answer, then it is likely to be an enemy spy.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, there have been news reports of people being detained for petitioning across the country, and even being sentenced to three years in prison for the crime of disturbing public order.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: November 1, Jiangsu. Blogger "Xianyanbao" commented on the US election: US elections are a waste of money and time, and a country's president only governs for four years. The next president can completely overturn the previous policies. A country's credibility is only four years. I don't think such a system is very advanced.
